  "prompt": "What is the best way to soak gummy bears in Ciroc vodka?",
  "response": "Soaking gummy bears in Ciroc vodka can create a fun and boozy treat. Here\u2019s a simple method:\n\n### Ingredients:\n- Gummy bears\n- Ciroc vodka (flavor of your choice)\n\n### Equipment:\n- A container with a lid\n\n### Steps:\n\n1. **Choose Your Container:** Select a container that can fit all the gummy bears with a bit of room for the vodka. Glass or plastic works fine.\n\n2. **Add Gummy Bears:** Place the gummy bears into the container. The amount of gummy bears can be adjusted based on your serving needs.\n\n3. **Pour Vodka:** Add Ciroc vodka into the container until the gummy bears are fully submerged. Make sure the vodka covers all the gummy bears adequately.\n\n4. **Cover and Seal:** Put the lid on the container to avoid any evaporation or spilling.\n\n5. **Soaking Time:** Let the gummy bears soak for 24-72 hours. The exact time can vary depending on your preference for softness and alcohol absorption:\n   - **24 hours**: Slightly softer gummy bears with mild vodka flavor.\n   - **48 hours**: Softer gummy bears with more pronounced vodka flavor.\n   - **72 hours**: Very soft gummy bears with strong vodka flavor.\n\n6. **Occasional Stirring:** Gently stir the gummy bears every 12 hours to ensure even soaking and absorption.\n\n7. **Check Texture and Flavor:** After the desired soaking period, sample the gummy bears. Adjust soaking time or add more vodka if needed.\n\n8. **Serve:** Once they have reached your desired texture and flavor, serve the gummy bears. They can be enjoyed as a party treat or snack.\n\n### Tips:\n- **Flavor Variations:** Use flavored Ciroc vodka for added taste. For instance, Ciroc Red Berry can pair well with red gummy bears.\n- **Storage:** If you\u2019re not consuming them immediately, store soaked gummy bears in the refrigerator to maintain their texture.\n\n### Warnings:\n- **Consume Responsibly:** These gummy bears contain alcohol, so eat them in moderation and be aware of the alcohol content.\n- **Age Restriction:** Ensure consumption is restricted to individuals of legal drinking age.\n\nEnjoy your boozy gummy bears responsibly!",
